description:
Nguyễn Thanh Tùng, stage name Sơn Tùng M-TP, is a Vietnamese singer, song writer as well as a actor. His 2012 and 2013 singles, "Cơn Mưa Ngang Qua" and "Em Của Ngày Hôm qua" are the milestones of starting of his career.

